      <title>centos修改hostname</title>
      <link href="/posts/f77ce5c3/"/>
      <url>/posts/f77ce5c3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="centos6修改hostname的方式"><a href="#centos6修改hostname的方式" class="headerlink" title="centos6修改hostname的方式"></a>centos6修改hostname的方式</h1><h2 id="重启生效"><a href="#重启生效" class="headerlink" title="重启生效"></a>重启生效</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ hostname                       # 查看当前的hostnmae</span><br><span class="line">HOSTNAME=fangbz.basic.01.host</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ vim /etc/sysconfig/network     # 编辑network文件修改hostname行（重启生效）</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ cat /etc/sysconfig/network     # 检查修改</span><br><span class="line">NETWORKING=yes</span><br><span class="line">HOSTNAME=hadoop000</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ vim /etc/hosts                   # 编辑hosts文件，给127.0.0.1添加hostname</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ cat /etc/hosts                   # 检查</span><br><span class="line">127.0.0.1 localhost localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4 hadoop000</span><br><span class="line">::1 localhost localhost.localdomain localhost6 localhost6.localdomain6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="立即生效"><a href="#立即生效" class="headerlink" title="立即生效"></a>立即生效</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ hostname hadoop000     # 设置当前的hostname(立即生效）</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ vim /etc/hosts                   # 编辑hosts文件，给127.0.0.1添加hostname</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ cat /etc/hosts                   # 检查</span><br><span class="line">127.0.0.1 localhost localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4 hadoop000</span><br><span class="line">::1 localhost localhost.localdomain localhost6 localhost6.localdomain6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="centos7修改hostname的方式"><a href="#centos7修改hostname的方式" class="headerlink" title="centos7修改hostname的方式"></a>centos7修改hostname的方式</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ hostnamectl set-hostname hadoop000     # 使用这个命令会立即生效且重启也生效</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ hostname                               # 查看下</span><br><span class="line">hadoop000</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ vim /etc/hosts                         # 编辑下hosts文件， 给127.0.0.1添加hostname</span><br><span class="line">[hadoop@hadoop000 ~]$ cat /etc/hosts                         # 检查</span><br><span class="line">127.0.0.1   localhost localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4 hadoop000</span><br><span class="line">::1         localhost localhost.localdomain localhost6 localhost6.localdomain6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
